CatDescriptText: Post 913 was located on the corner of Frankstown Avenue and Braddock Avenue in Homewood Brushton.
TitMainTitle: Man wearing military uniform and hat with number "201" standing behind group of tables pushed together with tablecloth, with gavel and bell on table, standing behind tabletop podium inscribed "Commander Sportsmen's Post 913" and seal inscribed "US American Legion" with "US American Legion Sportsmen's Post 913" painted on wall, in Post 913 in Homewood Brushton.
